            By continuing to access or use our Service after those revisions become effective, you agree to be bound by the revised terms. If you do not agree to the new terms, please stop using the Service.
          </p>
          
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-800 mt-10 mb-4">8. Contact Us</h2>
          
          <p class="text-gray-600 mb-6">
            If you have any questions about these Terms, please contact us at legal@fortifysecurity.com.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <!-- Quick Links -->
      <div class="flex justify-center space-x-6 mb-12">
        <a href="/privacy" class="text-primary-600 hover:text-primary-500 font-medium inline-flex items-center">
